 implementation of gst system will result in the rise of gdp ratio in the country its implementation will not only make the procedure of tax payment easy but also curb tax evasion all the indirect taxes will be included in this bill as a result making tax system simple and transparent and ultimately prove beneficial not only to the states and centre but  also  to  commerce  and  trade  sectors  this  bill  will  strengthen  the  growing economy of our developing country  